Package controller

Class MainScreenController

java.lang.Object
controller.MainScreenController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainScreenController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller class that provides logic for the application to run Allows for users to search, add, and delete both parts and products and allow for searching for both as well

Corey
